entry.summary:
Vendor: Egg Solutions
Type: FOOD

Egg Solutions - Pasteurized Liquid Whole Eggs - 20 Kg

Quickly and easily prepare scrambled eggs, omelets, and batter, with these fresh liquid eggs. These liquid eggs are shell-less and ready to use right out of the container. They are pasteurized and homogenized for safety, and have added citric acid to preserve the natural egg color.

With these liquid eggs, you'll be able to replace the tedious process of cracking and mixing eggs, with a simple pour from the container. Use them in any recipe that calls for eggs! An easy-to-read conversion chart is printed right on the carton, in English so you'll always know exactly how much liquid egg product to use in place of shell eggs. With these liquid eggs, you'll be able to offer a high protein, low calorie food, without all the labor.
